msgctxt "2440"
msgid "Mei Hua"
msgstr "Mei Hua"

msgctxt "2444"
msgid "Tanimura"
msgstr "Tanimura"

msgctxt "68_Mei Hua"
msgid "Dad and the others went to the outskirts of Senryo Avenue..."
msgstr "Papá y los otros fueron a las afueras de la Avenida Senryo..."

msgctxt "80_Mei Hua"
msgid "Ma-chan, we need to hurry!"
msgstr "Ma-chan, ¡tenemos que darnos prisa!"

msgctxt "92_Mei Hua"
msgid "You think my dad is okay!?"
msgstr "¿¡Crees que mi papá está bien!?"

msgctxt "104_Mei Hua"
msgid "Ma-chan! Hurry! We gotta go!"
msgstr "¡Ma-chan! ¡Deprisa! ¡Tenemos que irnos!"

msgctxt "116_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, let's go. Make sure to stick close!"
msgstr "Sí, vamonos. ¡Asegúrate de seguirme de cerca!"

msgctxt "128_Mei Hua"
msgid "Okay! Don't leave me behind, Ma-chan."
msgstr "¡Vale! No me dejes atrás, Ma-chan."

msgctxt "140_Tanimura"
msgid "Don't worry, Zhao-san's not that soft. You said it was the outskirts of Senryo Avenue? Follow me!"
msgstr "No te preocupes, Zhao-san no es tan blando. ¿Las afueras de la Avenida Senryo dijiste? ¡Sígueme!"

msgctxt "152_Mei Hua"
msgid "Okay! Don't leave me behind, Ma-chan."
msgstr "¡Vale! No me dejes atrás, Ma-chan."

msgctxt "164_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, I'm sure he's okay. You said it was the outskirts of Senryo Avenue? Let's move!"
msgstr "Sí, estoy seguro de que está bien. ¿Dijiste que era en las afuera de la Avenida Senryo? ¡Vamos!"

msgctxt "176_Mei Hua"
msgid "Okay! Don't leave me behind, Ma-chan."
msgstr "¡Vale! No me dejes atrás, Ma-chan."

msgctxt "188_Tanimura"
msgid "Calm down. I'm sure he's fine. You said it was the outskirts of Senryo Avenue?"
msgstr "Calmate. Seguro que está bien. ¿Dijiste que era en las afueras de la Avenida Senryo?"

msgctxt "200_Mei Hua"
msgid "Yeah... Maybe I'm being punished for not eating my shitake mushrooms yesterday..."
msgstr "Sí... Quizá me estén castigando por no comer mis setas shitake ayer..."

msgctxt "212_Tanimura"
msgid "You're worrying too much. Let's go!"
msgstr "Te preocupas demasiado. ¡Vamos!"

